# MegaLinter build image - not a production container
DS-0002
DS-0026

# DS-0001: "specify a tag in the FROM statement" for the distroless runtime
# image (gcr.io/distroless/cc-debian12). Distroless publishes no semver tags,
# and we keep the runtime on floating latest so each build pulls the newest
# patched layer. trivy still flags this, and the bundled trivy version (shipped
# inside the MegaLinter image) cannot be upgraded to a build that treats
# distroless better, so we suppress it here. Mirrors the hadolint DL3006 ignore
# in .linters/.hadolint.yaml.
DS-0001

# `lru` 0.15.0 is pulled in transitively by `walkers` 0.42.
# Walkers is pinned to 0.42 (see CLAUDE.md: highest version on egui 0.31;
# upgrading walkers requires upgrading egui, out of scope for this batch).
# Severity: LOW. Stacked-borrows invariant in IterMut; we don't call IterMut
# on the tile cache. Revisit when walkers/egui are bumped.
GHSA-rhfx-m35p-ff5j

# `thrift` 0.17.0 — no fixed upstream version published yet.
# Severity: MEDIUM. Pulled in via parquet/arrow stack.
# Memory allocation with excessive size value; only reachable when parsing
# untrusted Thrift payloads, which Octa does not accept directly (it reads
# Parquet via the arrow/parquet crates which use thrift for metadata, where
# the file's own metadata cap bounds the allocation). Revisit when the
# upstream advisory publishes a fixed crate version.
CVE-2026-43868

# `rustls-webpki` 0.101.7 — pulled in transitively via the MSSQL driver
# `tiberius` 0.12.3 (the latest release) -> `tokio-rustls` 0.24 -> `rustls`
# 0.21. tiberius has not published a release on newer rustls, so there is no
# upgrade path from our side. The HIGH advisory is a DoS panic when parsing a
# malformed CRL BIT STRING; Octa connects to user-configured SQL Server
# instances (trust_cert for password auth) and does not perform CRL validation
# against untrusted certificate revocation lists, so the panic path is not
# reachable in practice. The two LOW findings are name-constraint parsing
# quirks in the same crate. Revisit when tiberius ships on rustls 0.23+.
GHSA-82j2-j2ch-gfr8
GHSA-965h-392x-2mh5
GHSA-xgp8-3hg3-c2mh
